<SECTION>プログラミング

<ENTRY>0-201-54979-4 The Design and Implementation of the 4.4 BSD Operating System
著者: Marshall Kirk McKusick, Keith Bostic, Michael J. Karels,
John S. Quarterman<br>
出版社: Addison Wesley, 1996. (ISBN 0-201-54979-4)<br>
